data.description: Looking for a home to make your own? This one owner, non-smoker, no pets home is in a great location close to Granger, Elkhart, Mishawaka, or South Bend. And it's in the PHM school district, Horizon elementary, Discovery Middle school and Penn High.  The two-story home with a large backyard and a basement ready to finish could be perfect for you! Seller will provide a home warranty with an acceptable offer.   Don’t let this one go by, schedule a showing with your realtor today.
